messages.title: Do not hold onto things that require a tight grip.
I did not come this far to only come this far.
Look how far you've come.
You should face the reality with a smile.
The art of life is not controlling what happens to us, but using what happens to us.
Don't let yesterday take up too much of today.
If you want the rainbow, you gotta put up with the rain!
One bad chapter doesn't mean your story is over.
What you plant now, you will harvest later.
The most effective way to do it, is to do it.
You are your best thing.
There is always something left to love.
Breathe, Darling, this is just a chapter, not your whole story.
The world is your oyster.
You are exactly where you are supposed to be.
No more hiding.
The best way to predict your future is to create it.
Get busy living or get busy dying.
The future belongs to those who believe in the beauty of their dreams.
The only impossible journey is the one you never begin.
The fortune you seek is in another cookie.
You think it is a secret, but they know.
You will live long enough to open many fortune cookies.
Do not mistake temptation for opportunity.
You do not need strength to let go of something. What you really need is understanding.
Fortune not found? Abort, Retry, Ignore.
Help! I am being held prisoner in a fortune cookie factory.
Big journeys begin with a single step.
All things are difficult before they are easy.
You will soon have an out of money experience.
Today it's up to you to create the peacefulness you long for.
Change can hurt, but it leads a path to something better.
Now is the time to try something new.
Wealth awaits you very soon.
Everyone agrees. You are the best.
It's better to be alone sometimes.
Sometimes you just need to lay on the floor.
Stop wishing. Start doing.
Your golden opportunity is coming shortly.
To be old and wise, you must first be young and stupid.
You are extremely loved. Don't worry :).
Back away from individuals who are impulsive.
If you do not do it excellently, do not do it at all.
Engage in group activities that further transformation.
A pleasant experience is ahead: do not pass it by.
The only way to have a friend is to be one.
Stop worrying and take a chance.
A foolish man listens to his heart. A wise man listens to cookies.
If we wait until we're ready, we'll be waiting for the rest of our lives.
Do it scared.
Are your never-ending thoughts racing? Better go catch it!
